snippet.textDisplay: A few years ago I had varicoceles that were pressing right on that main nerve for my left testicle, I started going into shock and nearly dying with increasing frequency from once a month for about 6 months...it was the worst experience of my life and the hours of pure suffering and agony where the pain was so intense I couldn't, couldn't even breathe, and despite the Promise I made to GOD years earlier to live, I was begging HIM with shear audacity to either kill me or save me already. Everything would go black right after my bowels had released in the most unnatural way possible. Felt like I was being burned alive while it was happeneing, those nerves reach right up into your gut and down the adjacent thigh to the halfway point. Thank GOD I somehow found the forum Demons in our Scrotum because I knew I had to get surgery or one of those times I wasn't gonna wake back up (that or I might honestly try to slit my own throat if only i'd have enough time before collapsing on the cool tile). Anyways turned out some guy got the copper coil insert for aesthetic reasons, had no pain before. Thing slips gets lodged in his testicle and there is no way to safely remove it, he ends up like me on a cane and prescription grade pain killers. We were both in our early 20's. If I had gone with that, I surely would died from pain.  I spent three years on a cane and still have to wear support straps. The docs wanted to put me on twice a month cortisone injections, but for the first two years I decided it was safer to just get drunk every single day on 101 wild turkey...i eventually threw up the lining of my esophagus or maybe stomach, it was bloody and smelled awful, so it only took about 2-4 shots a day to walk around normally, unless a little attack hit me again.  Worst time in my life period. Lost my job, the woman I thought I was gonna marry left my ass right before the operation knowing I had a phobia of this kind of crap before anything even happened, and didn't even check tomake sure I didn't have a heart attack on the table or lose the whole testicle.  Trust me dude I know exactly what that conveniently forgotten circle of hell is like and yes it still haunts me to this day, (concrete toothpicks shooting through the veins) but you're stronger than me Nogla. Glad your still alive.
